TICKET_AVERAGE_SUBCATEGORIES: Ø price of products sold in the subcategories
TITLE: title
TT_AMZ_ALL_CATEGORIES: the category in which the product is listed
TT_AMZ_ASIN: the ASIN that should be searched for
TT_AMZ_AVAILABLE: Choose whether the product should be available or not. You can thus limit searches, e.g. to search only for products which are currently unavailable.
TT_AMZ_BRAND: Filter the search for products offered under this brand
TT_AMZ_BSR: Limit the search so that only products are displayed whose Best Seller rank lies within a defined range
TT_AMZ_CATEGORY: You can limit the search to one or more categories
TT_AMZ_COMPETITORS: Limit the search so that only products are displayed whose number of sellers lies within a certain range
TT_AMZ_EAN: the EAN that should be searched for
TT_AMZ_MERCHANT: Filter the search for products which are offered by this seller
TT_AMZ_MERCHANT_BUYBOX: Shows whether the selected seller has the Buy Box for the product
TT_AMZ_MERCHANT_COMPANY: the company name of the seller
TT_AMZ_MERCHANT_COMPANY_TYPE: the company type of the seller
TT_AMZ_MERCHANT_ID: the ID under which the seller is listed on Amazon
TT_AMZ_MERCHANT_PRIME: Shows whether the selected seller is offering the product as Prime/FBA
TT_AMZ_MERCHANT_SALES_24_HOURS: the number of sales by the seller within a 24-hour period
TT_AMZ_MERCHANT_SALES_30_DAYS: the number of sales by the seller within a 30-day period
TT_AMZ_MERCHANT_SALES_7_DAYS: the number of sales by the seller within a 7-day period
TT_AMZ_MERCHANT_SPRICE: the price at which the seller is offering the product
TT_AMZ_MERCHANT_STOCK: shows the current condition of the product for the given seller
TT_AMZ_PACKAGE_DIMENSION: the dimensions of the shipping parcel
TT_AMZ_PACKAGE_WEIGHT: the weight of the shipping parcel
TT_AMZ_PRIME: here you can limit your search to Prime products, or exclude these
TT_AMZ_PRIME_COMPETITORS: limit the search so that only products are displayed whose number of PRIME sellers falls within a certain range
TT_AMZ_RATING: limit the search so that only products are displayed whose current rating falls within a certain range
TT_AMZ_REVIEWS: limit the search so that only products are displayed whose current number of reviews falls within a certain range
TT_AMZ_SEO: limit the search so that only products are displayed whose SEO rating falls within a certain range
TT_AMZ_SOLD_BY_AMAZON: here you can select to search only for products which are sold by Amazon, or exclude these products
TT_AMZ_SPONSORED_PRODUCTS: You can limit the search for products for which Sponsored Products are activated, or exclude these
TT_AMZ_SPRICE: limit the search so that only products are displayed whose price falls within a certain range
TT_AMZ_TITLE: filter the search for products whose titles include this term
TT_AMZ_TYPE: here you can limit your search to PARENT, CHILDREN, or STANDALONE products, or exclude these
TT_CHART_Y_PERCENT_X_PRICE: [Y]% of products with a price between [X] and [X2]
TT_CHART_Y_PERCENT_X_RATING: [Y]% of products with a rating between [X] and [X2] stars
TT_CHART_Y_PRODUCTS_X_PRICE: [Y] products with a price between [X] and [X2]
TT_KEYWORD: the keyword for which the product ranks, or which could be relevant for the product
TT_KEYWORD_CHANGE: the change in keyword position for the selected keyword compared to the last query
TT_KEYWORD_COMPETITION: shows the level of competition for the selected keyword
TT_KEYWORD_POSITION: the position in all search results at which the product ranks with the given keyword
TT_KEYWORD_POSITION_REL: the position in Sponsored Ads at which the product ranks with the given keyword
TT_KEYWORD_RELEVANCE: the relevance of the keyword in relation to the product or its competing products
TT_REVIEW: the review written by the reviewer
TT_REVIEWER_ID: the Amazon internal ID of the reviewer
TT_REVIEW_COMMENTS: the number of comments on the selected review
TT_REVIEW_DATE: the day the review was written
TT_REVIEW_HAS_VIDEOS: shows whether the reviewer has also posted a video
TT_REVIEW_IMAGES: the number of images made available by the reviewers
TT_REVIEW_RATING: the rating given by the reviewer
TT_REVIEW_USEFULLS: the number of users who have found the selected review helpful
TT_TABLE_AMZ_AMASCORE: the current AMASCORE of the product. The higher the value, the better the product ranks for the relevant keywords
TT_TABLE_AMZ_AVG_POSITION: the ∅ position within which the search results at which the product currently ranks
TT_TABLE_AMZ_BSR: The current Bestseller rating of the product within its main category
TT_TABLE_AMZ_CATEGORY: the main category of the product
TT_TABLE_AMZ_COLOR: the color indication of the product
TT_TABLE_AMZ_KEYWORDS: the number of keywords for which the product currently ranks
TT_TABLE_AMZ_MERCHANT: the seller of the product who currently has it in the Buy Box
TT_TABLE_AMZ_PRIME: indicates whether the offer in the Buy Box is offered through Prime (FBA)
TT_TABLE_AMZ_REVIEWS: the number of ratings given for the product
TT_TABLE_AMZ_SALES_24_HOURS: the number of sales of the product in a 24-hour period
TT_TABLE_AMZ_SALES_30_DAYS: the number of sales of the product in a 30-day period
TT_TABLE_AMZ_SALES_7_DAYS: the number of sales of the product in a 7-day period
TT_TABLE_AMZ_SEO: the optimization rating (SEO value) of the listing
TT_TABLE_AMZ_SIZE: the size indication of the product (e.g. "60cm")
TT_TABLE_AMZ_SPRICE: the sales prices of the product in the Buy Box
TT_TABLE_AMZ_STOCK: Shows the current inventory of the product in which the inventory is combined over all sellers of this product
TT_TABLE_AMZ_TURNOVER_24_HOURS: and ecclesiastical and other religious associations (excluding social services and sports)
TT_TABLE_KEYWORD_HITS: the number of products found for the given keyword
TT_TABLE_SPA_HITS: the number of Sponsored Product Ads found in the top 100 search results
